00633           state.scan.builder.add_cell_interval(ci.start_row.c_str(),
00634               ci.start_column.c_str(), ci.start_inclusive, ci.end_row.c_str(),
00635               ci.end_column.c_str(), ci.end_inclusive);
00636           ci.clear();
00637           row.clear();
00638           column.clear();
00639           state.scan.current_relop = 0;

00641       }

00645     struct scan_set_row {

00647       void operator()(char const *str, char const *end) const {

00649         trim_if(state.scan.current_rowkey, is_any_of("'\""));
00650         if (state.scan.current_relop != 0) {

00669             if (state.scan.current_ri.start_set)
00670               HT_THROW(Error::HQL_PARSE_ERROR, "Bad row expressions.");
00671             state.scan.current_ri.set_start(state.scan.current_rowkey, false);
00672             break;
00673           case RELOP_GE:
00674             if (state.scan.current_ri.start_set)
00675               HT_THROW(Error::HQL_PARSE_ERROR, "Bad row expressions.");

00677             break;
00678           case RELOP_SW:

00680               HT_THROW(Error::HQL_PARSE_ERROR, "Bad row expressions.");
00681             state.scan.current_ri.set_start(state.scan.current_rowkey, true);
00682             str = state.scan.current_rowkey.c_str();
00683             end = str + state.scan.current_rowkey.length();
00684             const char *ptr;
00685             for (ptr = end - 1; ptr > str; --ptr) {
00686               if (uint8_t(*ptr) < 0xffu) {
00687                 String temp_str(str, ptr - str);
00688                 temp_str.append(1, (*ptr) + 1);
00689                 state.scan.current_ri.set_end(temp_str, false);
00690                 break;
00691               }
00692             }
00693             if (ptr == str) {
00694               state.scan.current_rowkey.append(4, (char)0xff);
00695               state.scan.current_ri.set_end(state.scan.current_rowkey, false);
00696             }
00697           }
00698           state.scan.current_rowkey_set = false;
00699           state.scan.current_relop = 0;
00700         }
00701         else {
00702           state.scan.current_rowkey_set = true;
00703           state.scan.current_cell_row.clear();
00704         }
00705       }
00706       ParserState &state;
00707     };

00806     struct scan_set_relop {
00807       scan_set_relop(ParserState &state, int relop)
00808         : state(state), relop(relop) { }
00809       void operator()(char const *str, char const *end) const {
00810         process();
00811       }
00812       void operator()(const char c) const {
00813         process();
00814       }
00815       void process() const {
00816         if (state.scan.current_timestamp_set) {
00817           switch (relop) {
00818           case RELOP_EQ:
00819             if (state.scan.start_time_set || state.scan.end_time_set)
00820               HT_THROW(Error::HQL_PARSE_ERROR, "Bad timestamp expression");
00821             state.scan.set_time_interval(state.scan.current_timestamp,
00822                                          state.scan.current_timestamp);
00823             break;
00824           case RELOP_GT:
00825             if (state.scan.end_time_set ||
00826                 (state.scan.start_time_set &&
00827                  state.scan.start_time() >= state.scan.current_timestamp))
00828               HT_THROW(Error::HQL_PARSE_ERROR, "Bad timestamp expression");
00829             state.scan.set_end_time(state.scan.current_timestamp);
00830             break;
00831           case RELOP_GE:
00832             if (state.scan.end_time_set ||
00833                 (state.scan.start_time_set &&
00834                  state.scan.start_time() > state.scan.current_timestamp))
00835               HT_THROW(Error::HQL_PARSE_ERROR, "Bad timestamp expression");
00836             state.scan.set_end_time(state.scan.current_timestamp + 1);
00837             break;
00838           case RELOP_LT:
00839             if (state.scan.start_time_set ||
00840                 (state.scan.end_time_set &&
00841                  state.scan.start_time() <= (state.scan.current_timestamp + 1)))
00842               HT_THROW(Error::HQL_PARSE_ERROR, "Bad timestamp expression");
00843             state.scan.set_start_time(state.scan.current_timestamp + 1);
00844             break;
00845           case RELOP_LE:
00846             if (state.scan.start_time_set ||
00847                 (state.scan.end_time_set &&
00848                  state.scan.end_time() <= state.scan.current_timestamp))
00849               HT_THROW(Error::HQL_PARSE_ERROR, "Bad timestamp expression");
00850             state.scan.set_start_time(state.scan.current_timestamp);
00851             break;
00852           case RELOP_SW:
00853             HT_THROW(Error::HQL_PARSE_ERROR, "Bad timestamp operator (=^)");
00854           }
00855           state.scan.current_timestamp_set = false;
00856           state.scan.current_relop = 0;
00857         }
00858         else if (state.scan.current_rowkey_set) {
00859           HT_ASSERT(state.scan.current_rowkey_set);
00860 
00861           switch (relop) {
00862           case RELOP_EQ:
00863             state.scan.current_ri.set_start(state.scan.current_rowkey, true);
00864             state.scan.current_ri.set_end(state.scan.current_rowkey, true);
00865             break;
00866           case RELOP_LT:
00867             state.scan.current_ri.set_start(state.scan.current_rowkey, false);
00868             break;
00869           case RELOP_LE:
00870             state.scan.current_ri.set_start(state.scan.current_rowkey, true);
00871             break;
00872           case RELOP_GT:
00873             state.scan.current_ri.set_end(state.scan.current_rowkey, false);
00874             break;
00875           case RELOP_GE:
00876             state.scan.current_ri.set_end(state.scan.current_rowkey, true);
00877             break;
00878           case RELOP_SW:
00879             HT_THROW(Error::HQL_PARSE_ERROR, "Bad use of operator (=^)");
00880           }
00881           state.scan.current_rowkey_set = false;
00882           state.scan.current_relop = 0;
00883         }
00884         else if (state.scan.current_cell_row.size()
00885                  && state.scan.current_ci.empty()) {
00886           String &row = state.scan.current_cell_row;
00887           String &column = state.scan.current_cell_column;
00888 
00889           switch (relop) {
00890           case RELOP_EQ:
00891             state.scan.current_ci.set_start(row, column, true);
00892             state.scan.current_ci.set_end(row, column, true);
00893             break;
00894           case RELOP_LT:
00895             state.scan.current_ci.set_start(row, column, false);
00896             break;
00897           case RELOP_LE:
00898             state.scan.current_ci.set_start(row, column, true);
00899             break;
00900           case RELOP_GT:
00901             state.scan.current_ci.set_end(row, column, false);
00902             break;
00903           case RELOP_GE:
00904             state.scan.current_ci.set_end(row, column, true);
00905           case RELOP_SW:
00906             HT_THROW(Error::HQL_PARSE_ERROR, "Bad use of operator (=^)");
00907           }
00908           row.clear();
00909           column.clear();
00910           state.scan.current_relop = 0;
00911         }
00912         else
00913           state.scan.current_relop = relop;
00914       }
00915       ParserState &state;
00916       int relop;
00917     };
